name: アノマロカリスモスマン

parameters:
Anomalocaris: (She's strong...! If I let her get the upper
hand, she's the scary type... Time to use my special fangs
to dampen her fighting spirit!)

Spectator: Did his fangs break it...? But Anomalocaris's
fangs are made of urethane... What kind of power would it
take to tear through Shark Duke's sharkskin mask...?

Bunny-chan: Oh no, Shark Duke's costume has been damaged!
Intentionally destroying a monster's body or costume is
strictly forbidden but—...

Anomalocaris: Mosmosmos... It wasn't on purpose, ya know?
The power of the Cambrian Needle was just stronger than
expected...

Spectator: Hey, isn't Shark Duke super cute?! Even with the
mask on, I thought she was a beauty, but she's way more
gorgeous than I imagined!

Spectator: No way, her face is too pretty... What is that...
an incredibly beautiful girl, isn't she?! Seriously
amazing...

Spectator: Wait a minute... I've seen that girl before!! She
works part-time at the Jagged Mart! Come to think of it,
that place is owned by Shark Broccoli...

Spectator: Eh, is that Sharkyama-chan?! Ah, definitely no
mistake!! It's the part-timer Sharkyama Memimi-chan... She's
usually a student and the student council president at
Doritoku Academy!

Spectator: Is that so?! Wow, she's still a student...
Sharkyama Memimi, the student council president of Doritoku
Academy... huh...

Memimi: (My identity has been exposed...! This is bad... my
real name and school are now known throughout the venue...
By tomorrow, this will spread all over town...!)

Anomalocaris: (Oh, she's been outed! The number one fear for
monsters in the rankings, having their face and real name
exposed...! This will definitely shake her up!)

Memimi: (Damn it... I need to stay calm now... focus on the
fight... What should I do... later, I'll think about it
later...!)

Memimi: Hmph... So what if my identity has been revealed...
Anomalocaris, are you that happy just because you broke my
mask? I have no intention of picking up a win from such a
trivial mishap... Let's resume the fight at once!

Anomalocaris: That's the spirit! It's clear I didn't break
it on purpose, right? You said it yourself, so let's get
back to it, resume!

Anomalocaris: (Hehehe... She's got too much pride to want a
victory without a fight... She seems composed, but my
Anomalocaris Fang attack must have planted fear deep in her
subconscious!!)
Bunny-chan: Then let's resume❤︎ Fight on!

Memimi: (Damn it... His technique doesn't matter, but having
my mask torn is a serious blow... It was custom-made and I
only have this one piece... My identity exposed too... This
is the worst...)
